  <diagram id="llm-vs-openclaw" name="⑥ 누가 만드는가 (가로 계층)">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1400" dy="900" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1480" pageHeight="840" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="t" value="누가 실제로 만드는가 : 가로 계층(Layer) 구조" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="15" width="1200" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="legend" value="왼쪽(토대)이 오른쪽(결과)을 받쳐주는 흐름 — 왼쪽에서 오른쪽으로 갈수록 '눈에 보이는 것'에 가까워집니다" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=12;fontColor=#666666;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="55" width="1200" height="25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tier3_title" value="③ OpenClaw 계층 — 토대" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#DAE8FC;gradientColor=#EAF2FB;strokeColor=#6C8EBF;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;fontSize=16;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=middle;align=center;arcSize=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="110" width="440" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tier3_body" value="무대 · 도구 · 기억을 제공&#10;&#10;• IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md&#10;   → LLM에게 성격/정체성을 부여&#10;&#10;• TOOLS.md + 실제 도구&#10;   → 웹 검색, 파일 조작 등 '실행' 능력 부여&#10;&#10;• agents/ 세션 기록&#10;   → 이전 대화를 기억하게 하는 메모리&#10;&#10;• 디스코드 채널 연동&#10;   → 답변을 실제 메시지로 주고받는 통로" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#DAE8FC;gradientColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#6C8EBF;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;fontSize=13;fontStyle=0;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacing=10;arcSize=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="180" width="440" height="490" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tier2_title" value="② LLM 계층 — 실제로 &quot;만드는&quot; 주체" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E1D5E7;gradientColor=#F3ECF6;strokeColor=#9673A6;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;fontSize=16;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=middle;align=center;arcSize=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="520" y="110" width="440" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tier2_body" value="openai/gpt-5.5&#10;&#10;• 텍스트를 생성하고, 질문에 답하고,&#10;   코드를 짜는 등 실질적인 콘텐츠 생성을&#10;   담당합니다&#10;&#10;• 오픈클로 자체는 언어 모델이 아닙니다&#10;&#10;• &quot;생각하는 뇌&quot;는 어디까지나 GPT입니다" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E1D5E7;gradientColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#9673A6;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;fontSize=13;fontStyle=0;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacing=10;arcSize=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="520" y="180" width="440" height="490" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tier1_title" value="① 결과물 계층 — 사용자에게 보이는 것" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#D5E8D4;gradientColor=#EAF5EA;strokeColor=#82B366;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;fontSize=16;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=middle;align=center;arcSize=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1000" y="110" width="440" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tier1_body" value="대화창에 실제로 나타나는 것&#10;&#10;• 답변&#10;&#10;• 코드&#10;&#10;• 보고서&#10;&#10;• 기타 최종 산출물" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#D5E8D4;gradientColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#82B366;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;fontSize=13;fontStyle=0;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacing=10;arcSize=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1000" y="180" width="440" height="490" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="a1" value="환경을 제공한다" style="edgeStyle=none;rounded=0;html=1;fontSize=13;endArrow=block;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#6C8EBF;strokeWidth=3;fontColor=#6C8EBF;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;" edge="1" parent="1" source="tier3_body" target="tier2_body">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="a2" value="생성한다" style="edgeStyle=none;rounded=0;html=1;fontSize=13;endArrow=block;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;strokeColor=#9673A6;strokeWidth=3;fontColor=#9673A6;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;" edge="1" parent="1" source="tier2_body" target="tier1_body">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="conclusion" value="💡 정리&#10;모델을 다른 LLM으로 바꿔도 ③ 계층(성격·도구·기억·연동)은 그대로 유지됩니다 — '요리사'만 바뀌고 '주방'은 그대로인 셈입니다." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#D6B656;fontSize=13;fontStyle=0;verticalAlign=middle;align=left;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="710" width="1400" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>